00:38:22.760 --> 00:38:28.000
<i>shelter him in the shelter of His wings forever.</i>

439
00:38:28.160 --> 00:38:32.680
<i>and bind his soul in the bond of life.</i>

440
00:38:32.920 --> 00:38:35.000
<i>His soul.</i>

441
00:38:35.080 --> 00:38:38.880
<i>the Lord is his inheritance.</i>

442
00:38:39.040 --> 00:38:45.360
<i>and may he rest in peace upon his resting place.</i>

443
00:38:45.600 --> 00:38:49.480
<i>and let us say Amen." -Blessed be God.
Amen. -Amen.</i>

444
00:38:52.080 --> 00:38:53.040
Congratulations.

445
00:39:13.280 --> 00:39:15.200
<i>"Magnified and sanctified be His great name."</i>
-Amen.

446
00:39:15.440 --> 00:39:16.760
<i>"In the world that He created according to His will.</i>

447
00:39:16.840 --> 00:39:19.440
<i>may He establish His kingdom and bring forth His redemption
and hasten His Messiah." -Amen.</i>

448
00:39:19.640 --> 00:39:22.320
<i>In your lifetimes and in your days
and in the life of all the House of Israel.</i>

449
00:39:22.520 --> 00:39:24.680
<i>speedily and soon.
and let us say Amen." -Amen.</i>

450
00:39:25.640 --> 00:39:27.920
<i>"May His great name be blessed
forever and to all eternity.</i>

451
00:39:28.360 --> 00:39:33.480
<i>Blessed and praised and glorified and exalted
and extolled and honored and elevated and lauded</i>

452
00:39:33.600 --> 00:39:35.240
<i>be the name of the Holy One. blessed be He."</i>
-Amen.

453
00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:38.680
<i>Beyond all blessings. songs.
praises and consolations</i>

454
00:39:38.760 --> 00:39:40.520
<i>that are uttered in the world. and let us say Amen."</i>
-Amen.

455
00:39:42.920 --> 00:39:45.800
<i>May there be abundant peace from heaven
and good life upon us</i>

456
00:39:45.880 --> 00:39:47.960
<i>and upon all His people Israel. and let us say Amen."</i>
-Amen.

457
00:39:55.480 --> 00:39:58.240
<i>He who makes peace in His heights.</i>

458
00:40:01.120 --> 00:40:03.680
<i>may He in His mercy make peace upon us
and upon all His people Israel.</i>

459
00:40:03.760 --> 00:40:05.080
<i>and let us say Amen." -Amen.</i>

